notes.title: Code availability
notes.p: The software’s used includes; Chemdraw software version 12.0.2, Spartan’14 (version 1.1.2), Material studio (V8) software, Pyrex software version, PADEL-Descriptor Software V2.20, and DTC data lab software, Microsoft word Office Excel 2013 version and Auto dock visualizer version 4.2,
